reviewText: The only reason I didn't give this 5 stars is because IT IS NOT DIAMOND EDITION!!

Arrived a little earlier than expected which I love, great quality (especially after using the VHS version for so long) and the first disc is mostly the original movie. Aside from the song "Human Again" being added that gives us more of a tour around the castle and makes me seriously want to start spring cleaning. :)
The 2nd disc has the alternate beginning and deleted scenes.
I love this movie ! It's the best ! Its worth getting  honestly can't go wrong.
Perfect exactly what I was looking for and speedy delivery!
This is my and my grandchildrens favorite movie. I had it on VHS and it broke we watched it so much.
I LOVE this movie it's Really good showing that people can change and it's a love story the best Disney movie ever made to me :-) :-)
One of Disney's best and an all time favorite.
